                    <div>
	<div class="mva">
		<img height="13" border="0" width="24" alt="" src="http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/nol/shared/img/v3/start_quote_rb.gif" />
		<b>This will be discussed by chief executives and others for some time to come and it will further reinforce the need for corporate asset protection systems</b>
		<img height="13" align="right" vspace="0" border="0" width="23" alt="" src="http://newsimg.bbc.co.uk/nol/shared/img/v3/end_quote_rb.gif" /><br clear="all"/>	</div>




</div>
                
                     
                    <div class="mva">
	<div>Richard Starnes<br />Computer security expert</div>


</div>
                
            </td>
